This is a great typographic starting point when creating web projects.  It covers all of the key elements that need to be styled.  Modifying this stylesheet makes it east to set up type that might be controlled by a CMS.  You'll be sure that you won't be surpirsed by clients using elements you didn't plan on.

More details here:
http://www.gethifi.com/blog/a-boilerplate-for-css-typography